title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 9 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – May 9 2022
description:
Biden blames his tanking economy on everyone else. Bill Maher makes some sane comments on abortion. Allie Beth Stuckey, host of the podcast "Relatable," and author of "You're Not Enough" breaks down the baby formula shortage, abortion debate and issues firing up America's moms. Kim Jong Un bans skinny jeans. What apparel would you ban?

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
